{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/Wishlist-and-Follow.gif?t=1628262790\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/01_FirstImpressions_short_600px.gif?t=1628262790\" /><br><br>Dive into a magical woven world on the back of your own carpet dragon! Explore the textile landscape, solve puzzles, challenge quirky creatures and unravel the great mysteries of a long forgotten past in <i>Weaving Tides</i>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique weaving gameplay</h2> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/DesGateDotPattern_600x178_veryShort.gif?t=1628262790\" /> Stitch and cut your way through the textile landscape. Use the weavers abilities to wrap up your foes and conquer tricky zelda-like dungeons and puzzles. Choose the weaver which fits your playstyle and outfit them with mystic embroideries to further enhance their abilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore a vibrant woven world</h2> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/LayersCompilation_600x178.gif?t=1628262790\" /> Dive into an enchanting, textile landscape and be swept away by the colorful cast of characters with fully hand painted portraits and the captivating musical score.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover hidden mysteries packed in a charming story</h2> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/Steam_CommunityUpdateBanner_SpunForestConversation_cut_small.png?t=1628262790\" /> Gather eccentric allies on Tass' quest to find his parents, assemble fragments of the past and eventually unveil the long forgotten secrets of the woven world.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Creative Playground Mode</h2> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/PlaygroundRibbons_600x178_veryShort.gif?t=1628262790\" /> Unlock new, colorful ribbons for your Weavers during the campaign and use them in the playground feature to freely stitch and create your own digital embroidery.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Awards</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1075170/extras/Awards_600x178_veryShort.gif?t=1628262790\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Silken Desert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/7f76af5f3e7b6af15e64dab788ab762e49203652.jpg"},{"name":"Leave a mark","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/385e83e558375176479edd22f53eff42955821ff.jpg"},{"name":"Tasty Bite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/679d3ed2f5c6b94979394d8842b911bd0c21d42b.jpg"},{"name":"Yapper Flip","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/c7195e89d7f03c59a65255947a7fb03865c28ad3.jpg"},{"name":"Baaaaa","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/06140c560bc94dc4dfe12741582c02827514c099.jpg"},{"name":"Helping Hand","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/5073d2089d2630543d587a00aee331234b79099d.jpg"},{"name":"Was that a Tongue?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/149f7dc9787483d1b85c8e140b1011b1c66fb150.jpg"},{"name":"Defeated the Dungeon Guardian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/0f4d454b95fa455e4fe5fb7bcb0dbf3d45c6ac77.jpg"},{"name":"Spun Forests","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1075170/ea05be19a08c08503d0690952e